{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM08_140.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x27,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Im...possible..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x5a,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No way..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x5a,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "We're like this again... I didn't think we'd turn back..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "The Cauldron of Knowledge... Was destroyed...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Most likely... Haha, looks like we don't have anything left."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Without the Cauldron, we're finished. We can't use alchemy anymore."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...We can never turn back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "...I can't believe it. How could we lose?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "...That's likely the difference between your desires."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Luard, your only goal was to master Ablation Alchemy. You used alchemy only for yourself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "However, Sophie is different. She has used alchemy earnestly, for the sake of others."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "She worked out of her wish to bring happiness to all people, including you and I."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy is the power of wishes. You should already know that the stronger the wish, the stronger that power grows."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Your selfish alchemy stood no chance of winning against Sophie's alchemy, and her wish to bring happiness to all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Haha... Hahahaha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...What? So you're saying everything we've done until now was for nothing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "We lost to a regular alchemist, and we can't use alchemy anymore. What was the point of our life?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "...It wasn't for nothing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Huh...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "It wasn't all for nothing. It's true that using Ablation Alchemy was a mistake."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "But your wish to save your village, together with Plachta, wasn't for nothing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "You shouldn't say that the dream you shared with Plachta in the past was for nothing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Sophie..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Here..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "This is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "It's the first item that you and Plachta made. Look at this, and remember your real dream."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "...Let's go, Atomina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Huh...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Let's go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Okay..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "...I wonder what those two will do now? I hope they understood..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "...Yes, they'll be fine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure they heard and understood what you wanted to tell them. I'm sure..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "...Yeah! You're right!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, Plachta... Let's go home."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Yes, let's go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Back to our atelier!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Back to our atelier!"
        }
    ]
}